<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12100] Run tests for all modules in QA run</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12100</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some tests in hbase-server module are flaky.&lt;br/&gt;
Currently tests in subsequent modules such as hbase-shell may be skipped if one or more tests from hbase-server module fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Chatting with Anoop, we think for JIRAs whose patch has incompatible change, it is important to detect failed test(s) in all modules.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can apply &apos;--fail-at-end&apos; option in runTests() method of test-patch.sh&lt;/p&gt;</description>
